ed="T" n="0884b10"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0884b10"/><head><date from-iso="+0936-12-05" key="j20632662067017" to-iso="+0947-03-14">晉</date><placeName key="PL000000023307"><anchor xml:id="beg0884sgsz7"/>東京<anchor xml:id="end0884sgsz7"/>相國寺</placeName><persName key="A013782">遵誨</persName>傳（<persName key="A013787">彥求</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0884b11"/><persName key="A013782">釋遵誨</persName>，姓<name>李</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000016494">譙郡</placeName>人也。祖世不仕，母<persName key="A019507">張<lb
ed="T" n="0884b12"/></persName>氏夢神人授<anchor xml:id="beg0884sgsz9"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0884sgsz9"/>寶珠，乃有娠焉。生且奇異，乳<lb
ed="T" n="0884b13"/>哺之時，善認人之喜慍。彌長，見寺觀，必任<lb
ed="T" n="0884b14"/>步遲迴<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1925"/>，顧<anchor xml:id="beg0884sgsz11"/>盻<anchor xml:id="end0884sgsz11"/>不捨。<ref type="date" target="#j20443242044707">年甫十一</ref>，<anchor xml:id="beg0884sgsz13"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0884sgsz13"/><placeName key="PL000000016486"><placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0884sgsz15"/>亳<anchor xml:id="end0884sgsz15"/>城</placeName><placeName>開元寺</placeName></placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0884b15"/><persName key="A013783">崇諲</persName>律主為師範矣。誦《法華經》，二周<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2262"/>畢部，<lb
ed="T" n="0884b16"/>由是勤於學問。殆<ref type="date" target="#j20476322047985">登弱冠</ref>，受于戒律，持彼<lb
ed="T" n="0884b17"/>律儀，確乎轉石<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2263"/>。尋師<placeName key="PL000000023581">西洛</placeName>，問道<placeName key="PL000000023340">梁園</placeName>，初<lb
ed="T" n="0884b18"/><anchor xml:id="beg0884002"/>于<anchor xml:id="end0884002"/><persName key="A013784">智潛<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>傳《法華經》，講精義入神<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2284"/>，雌黃<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2264"/><lb
ed="T" n="0884b19"/>滿口。<date from-iso="+0908-02-10" key="j20527402053094" to-iso="+0909-01-29">梁<name>開平</name>二年戊辰歲</date>，止<placeName key="PL000000023308"><placeName>相國寺</placeName><placeName>藥師院</placeName></placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0884b20"/>首講所業<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2265"/>。至<placeName key="PL000000057656">後唐</placeName><date from-iso="+0931-01-27" key="j20611272061509" to-iso="+0932-02-13"><name>長興</name>二年辛卯歲</date>，門徒相<lb
ed="T" n="0884b21"/>續請其訓導，已周一十九遍，升其堂者二<lb
ed="T" n="0884b22"/>十餘人。洎<date from-iso="+0937-02-18" key="j20633412063694" to-iso="+0938-02-06"><name>天福</name>二年</date>，有<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺山</placeName><persName key="A013785">繼顒<roleName>大師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0884b23"/>精達《華嚴》大經，躬入<placeName key="PL000000023327">東京</placeName>，進<persName key="A006579">晉祖</persName>降聖節<ptr target="#n2047"/><lb
ed="T" n="0884b24"/>功德。<persName key="A013782">誨</persName>仰<persName key="A013785">顒<roleName>師</roleName></persName>辯浪經江，下風<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1108"/>趨附，乃允講<lb
ed="T" n="0884b25"/>宣。<persName key="A013782">誨</persName>善下百川，蔚成藏海矣！<placeName key="PL000000023327">梁</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000025555">宋</placeName>之<anchor xml:id="beg0884sgsz19"/>間<anchor xml:id="end0884sgsz19"/>以<lb
ed="T" n="0884b26"/><persName key="A013785">顒</persName>罷唱，請<persName key="A013782">誨</persName>敷揚<ptr target="#n3443"/>，𢈈匝<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2266"/>虛堂，緇素雲萃，<anchor xml:id="beg0884003"/>募<anchor xml:id="end0884003"/><lb
ed="T" n="0884b27"/>四眾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g98"/>鐫石壁《華嚴經》一部於講殿三面焉！嗟<lb
ed="T" n="0884b28"/>其油素<ptr type="glossary" target="#g309"/>，易罹炎上<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2267"/>之災；刻此貞珉<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2190"/>，寧患白<lb
ed="T" n="0884b29"/>蟫<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2268"/>之食。工未告終，所施已足。又召僧俗人<pb ed="T" n="0884c" xml:id="T50.2061.0884c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0884c01"/>各念一卷，得二百四十人，成三部<!-- 八十華嚴 -->，四季建<lb
ed="T" n="0884c02"/>經會，近二十年，更無<anchor xml:id="beg0884sgsz21"/>間<anchor xml:id="end0884sgsz21"/>曠。復別施鬼神水<lb
ed="T" n="0884c03"/>陸法食，皆勸勵莊嚴菩提心行矣！朝廷崇<lb
ed="T" n="0884c04"/>重，旌表其功，賜號<persName key="A013782">真行大師</persName>。<date key="j20662802066280" when-iso="+0945-03-07"><name>開運</name>二年乙<anchor xml:id="beg0884sgsz23"/><choice resp="PC-JK-MB"><sic>已</sic><corr>巳</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0884sgsz23"/><lb
ed="T" n="0884c05"/>歲正月十六日</date>示疾，策杖教誡門弟子訖，右<lb
ed="T" n="0884c06"/>脇而臥，口誦佛名，斯須長逝矣。享壽七十<lb
ed="T" n="0884c07"/>一，法臘五十一。門生奉遺旨葬于<placeName key="PL000000058505">隨河</placeName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0884c08"/>北，寺莊東原也。次有<placeName key="PL000000011483"><placeName>杭州</placeName><placeName>龍華寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A013787">釋彥求</persName>，姓<lb
ed="T" n="0884c09"/><name>葉</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000014972">縉雲</placeName>人也。<date notBefore-iso="+0915-12-22" key="j20556122057612" notAfter-iso="+0921-06-13"><name>梁</name><name>貞明</name>中</date>納戒，造<persName key="A001248">景霄</persName>律<lb
ed="T" n="0884c10"/>席，逈見毘尼祕邃，方將傳講，俄悟<persName key="A017448"><anchor xml:id="beg0884004"/><choice resp="PC-JK-MB"><sic>呇</sic><corr>沓</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0884004"/>婆<lb
ed="T" n="0884c11"/><roleName>羅漢</roleName></persName>，反求堅固法<ptr target="#n3444"/>。乃遊<placeName key="PL000000056838">閩嶺</placeName>，得<persName key="A003890">長慶<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0884c12"/>心決。迴<placeName key="PL000000008355">浙</placeName>，受<placeName key="PL000000012388">丹丘</placeName>人請，居<placeName key="PL000000011665">六通院</placeName>，其道望<lb
ed="T" n="0884c13"/>惟馨，與夫申椒、菌桂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2269"/>爭，其芬烈矣。<placeName key="PL000000008355">漢南國</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0884c14"/>王<persName key="A006774">錢</persName>氏<ptr target="#n2048"/>欽其高行，命住<placeName key="PL000000011452">功臣院</placeName>。末歸州治<lb
ed="T" n="0884c15"/><placeName key="PL000000011483">龍華寺</placeName>，聚徒開演。<persName key="A013787">求</persName>好營眾事，務必身先，<lb
ed="T" n="0884c16"/>唯以利人為急，受施必歸。常住房無關鍵，<lb
ed="T" n="0884c17"/>笥<ptr type="glossary" target="#g609"/>無扃鐍<ptr type="glossary" target="#g673"/>；不容尼眾<anchor xml:id="beg0884sgsz25"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0884sgsz25"/>謁，不苟聲勢<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2270"/>。常<lb
ed="T" n="0884c18"/>屬度戒，四遠人聚，日供累千僧食，未甞告<lb
ed="T" n="0884c19"/>匱言。前後計飯鉅萬人焉！<date notBefore-iso="+0960-02-09" key="j20717322073130" notAfter-iso="+0963-12-08"><name>宋</name><name>建隆</name>中</date>終于<lb
ed="T" n="0884c20"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000011483">住寺</ref>云。</p>
